author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Adrian Quesada performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded September 2, 2025.

Songs:  
Puedes Decir De Mi (with Gaby Moreno) 00:41
El Muchacho De Los Ojos Tristes (with Gaby Moreno) 03:58
Hoy Que Llueve (with Trish Toledo) 08:31
No Juego (with Angelica Garcia) 14:38
Ídolo (with Angelica Garcia) 18:17

Adrian Quesada - Guitar
